>
> ***Tail.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +12 to hit, reach 15ft., one target. *Hit:* 11 (1d8 + 7) bludgeoning damage.
>
> ***Frightful Presence.*** Each creature of the dragon's choice that is within 120 feet of the dragon and aware of it must succeed on a DC 19 Wisdom saving throw or become frightened for 1 minute. A creature can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success. If a creature's saving throw is successful or the effect ends for it, the 
>
