<br/>    DC 16 Dexterity saving throw, taking 24 (7d6) force 
<br/>    damage plus 10 (3d6) cold damage on a failed save, 
<br/>    or half as much damage on a successful one. 
> <br/> In addition, any creature damaged by the breath must 
