> <br/> 3/day each: *dream*, *hypnotic pattern* , *locate animals  or <br/>      plants*, *suggestion*
> <br/> 1/day each: *animal shapes*, *conjure fey*
> 
>
> ### Actions
> ***Multiattack.*** The wyrm can use its Frightful Presence. It then makes two attacks: one with its bite and one with its claws.
>
