>
> ### Actions
> ***Multiattack.*** The dragonspawn makes two greatsword attacks.
>
> ***Bite.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.
*Hit:* 7 (1d8 + 3) piercing damage.
>
> ***Greatsword.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +5 to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. *Hit:* 10 (2d6 + 3) slashing damage.

