> ***Blurry Vision (Recharge 6).*** The drakonid can impose disadvantage on an attack that would hit it. If the attack misses the drakonid, the creature must make a DC 13 Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, the creature becomes incapacitated until the start of its next turn. 

